scripts.prepublish: npm run generate-browser-core && npm run generate-browser-full
scripts.generate-browser-core: node tools/build.js --features=core --no-debug --release --zalgo --browser --minify && mv js/browser/bluebird.js js/browser/bluebird.core.js && mv js/browser/bluebird.min.js js/browser/bluebird.core.min.js

scripts.test: npm run lint && npm run test-ci && npm run test-browser

scripts.build: mkdir -p lib && rm -rf lib/* && node_modules/.bin/coffee --compile -m --output lib/ src/

scripts.mocha-test: npm run mocha-node-test && npm run mocha-browser-test
scripts.test: npm run-script lint && npm run nodeunit-test && npm run mocha-test
scripts.lint: jshint lib/*.js test/*.js perf/*.js && jscs lib/*.js test/*.js perf/*.js
scripts.coveralls: nyc npm test && nyc report --reporter=text-lcov | coveralls

scripts.ci-test: npm run test && npm run browser && npm run report

scripts.test-travis: istanbul cover node_modules/mocha/bin/_mocha --report lcovonly -- --reporter dot test/test.js

scripts.lint: npm run jscs && npm run eslint

scripts.test: tar --xform 's/^package/readable-stream-1.0/' -zxf readable-stream-1.0.*.tgz && tar --xform 's/^package/readable-stream-1.1/' -zxf readable-stream-1.1.*.tgz && node test.js; rm -rf readable-stream-1.?/

scripts.postpublish: git push origin --all; git push origin --tags

scripts.pretest: npm run --silent readme && npm run --silent lint
scripts.dist: mkdirp dist && browserify --standalone Qs lib/index.js > dist/qs.js

scripts.test-regen: npm run profclean && TEST_REGEN=1 node test/00-setup.js

scripts.version: npm run toc && git add README.md

scripts.postpublish: git push origin --all; git push origin --tags

scripts.browser: browserify -t browserify-istanbul test/lib/browserify_adjustment.js test/test-*.js | obake --coverage | tap-spec

scripts.version: npm run toc && git add README.md

scripts.ci: tap test/parallel/*.js test/ours/*.js --tap | tee test.tap && node test/verify-dependencies.js

scripts.semantic-release: semantic-release pre && npm publish && semantic-release post

scripts.eslint: if-node-version ">=4" eslint lib/*.js lib/compile/*.js spec/*.js scripts
scripts.bundle-all: del-cli dist && npm run bundle && npm run bundle-regenerator && npm run bundle-nodent
scripts.test-browser: del-cli .browser && npm run bundle-all && scripts/prepare-tests && npm run test-karma
scripts.test: npm run jshint && npm run eslint && npm run test-ts && npm run build && npm run test-cov && if-node-version 4 npm run test-browser
scripts.prepublish: npm run build && npm run bundle-all

scripts.fetch: gnode scripts/fetch-apache && gnode scripts/fetch-iana && gnode scripts/fetch-nginx
scripts.update: npm run fetch && npm run build

scripts.test: npm run eslint && nyc npm run test-spec

scripts.ci: tap test/parallel/*.js test/ours/*.js --tap | tee test.tap && node test/verify-dependencies.js

scripts.build: uglifyjs nacl.js -c -m -o nacl.min.js && uglifyjs nacl-fast.js -c -m -o nacl-fast.min.js
scripts.test-node-all: make -C test/c && tape test/*.js test/c/*.js | faucet
scripts.test-browser: NACL_SRC=${NACL_SRC:='nacl.min.js'} && npm run build-test-browser && cat $NACL_SRC test/browser/_bundle.js | tape-run | faucet
scripts.build-test-browser: browserify test/browser/init.js test/*.js | uglifyjs -c -m -o test/browser/_bundle.js 2>/dev/null && browserify test/browser/init.js test/*.quick.js | uglifyjs -c -m -o test/browser/_bundle-quick.js 2>/dev/null
scripts.test: npm run test-node-all && npm run test-browser
npm run eslint && nyc npm run test-spec
npm run eslint && npm run test-ts && npm run test-cov
